==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Honk
<hw>Honk</hw> <pr>(h⟦ocr⟧⟦nsm⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
make a sound like the honk of a goose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>To sound the horn on
an automobile or other motor vehicle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>honker</ent>⟦br⟧
